@end deffn

@deffn Function minor-mode-global-p name
Return whether @var{name} supports globalized behavior.
@end deffn

@deffn Function global-minor-mode-set name state
Enable or disable @var{name} globally.  Disabling removes global-sourced
activations while preserving explicit buffer-local re-enables.
@end deffn

@deffn Function global-minor-mode-active-p name
Return whether @var{name} is globally active.
@end deffn

@deffn Function global-minor-mode-list-active
